sequenceDiagram
    participant C as CommitLog
    participant R as ReputMessageService
    participant D as DefaultMessageStore
    participant Q as ConsumeQueueStore
    participant I as IndexService
    participant L as LongPolling Listener

    C-->>R: 新增物理记录
    R->>C: getData(reputFromOffset)
    R->>C: checkMessageAndReturnSize
    R->>D: doDispatch(dispatchRequest)
    D->>Q: 构建逻辑队列单元
    D->>I: 构建 Key 索引
    R->>L: notifyMessageArriveIfNecessary
    R->>R: reputFromOffset += messageSize
